10
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:39,180
=Episode 18=

11
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,180
(Zhu Mansion)

12
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:43,500
(Opera)
Phoenix Hairpin?

13
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:44,920
Tonight's first opera

14
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:46,590
is Phoenix Hairpin.

15
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:47,950
Do you mean to

16
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:49,790
show everyone in Lingshui

17
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,640
that I'm as evil as Mrs. Lu in it,

18
00:01:51,910 --> 00:01:53,590
breaking up you and my son?

19
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:54,670
I wouldn't dare.

20
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,430
I had left for charity when operas

21
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:57,430
needed to be chosen.

22
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,600
When I returned,

23
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,070
I heard you had decided on them.

24
00:02:00,070 --> 00:02:01,080
Stop lying!

25
00:02:01,910 --> 00:02:03,030
Are you saying

26
00:02:03,150 --> 00:02:04,480
I chose that one in particular

27
00:02:04,530 --> 00:02:05,590
to insult myself?

28
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,360
You're disrespectful to me.

29
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:09,270
I can have my son divorce you.

30
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,510
Mother, it really wasn't me.

31
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:17,160
Mother, I'm not Lu Wuguan.

32
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,310
I won't listen to you to divorce Yi.

33
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:20,640
It'll never happen, Mother.

34
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:22,950
Get up, Yi.

35
00:02:29,710 --> 00:02:30,990
I ordered that opera,

36
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,360
not Yi.

37
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,200
You...

38
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,880
You're still covering for her?

39
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:36,840
If you were

40
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,950
a kind mother-in-law,

41
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,390
you wouldn't fear rumors.

42
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:40,670
In the last few days,

43
00:02:40,870 --> 00:02:42,030
Yi went here and there

44
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,600
for the Water Festival.

45
00:02:43,710 --> 00:02:45,160
Not only did you not help her,

46
00:02:45,470 --> 00:02:46,780
but you also kept picking on her.

47
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,310
How unfilial!

48
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,150
That's enough.

49
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,120
Don't be mad, Mother.

50
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,280
It's all my fault.

51
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,120
Mrs. Ziyu!

52
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,150
Mrs. Ziyu!

53
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,400
Mrs. Ziyu,

54
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,710
the Caiyun Troupe is a mess.

55
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:59,270
- You kicked me!
- Stop, you two!

56
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,640
You vamp!

57
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,630
Stop, ladies!

58
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:04,550
That's enough!

59
00:03:04,650 --> 00:03:06,040
- I'm begging you!
- I'll kill you!

60
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,360
- How dare you!
- It's my fault!

61
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,590
It's my bad, alright?

62
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:10,180
I shouldn't have given you that lip balm.

63
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:11,000
- I'm sorry!
- Stop.

64
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:11,840
It's your fault!

65
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:19,160
It's a big day today.

66
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,440
You two are the stars of the Caiyun Troupe.

67
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,110
Why are you fighting?

68
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:25,000
What's going on?

69
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,060
Sorry for the trifle.

70
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:28,600
Trifle?

71
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,080
Look at my face!

72
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,390
She caused it!

73
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:36,500
(Yanniang, Caiyun Troupe)

74
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:40,600
It's an allergy caused by yams.

75
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,040
She's taken the medicine,

76
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:44,090
but it'll take six hours

77
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,710
at least to reduce the swelling.

78
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:47,310
That's too long.

79
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,560
I have to go on stage

80
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:49,400
in less than two.

81
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:51,920
Are there other ways, Physician?

82
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:53,760
There's nothing else I can do.

83
00:03:54,150 --> 00:03:54,990
Good day.

84
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,680
Where was yam

85
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,080
added to the lip balm?

86
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,030
Ask her!

87
00:04:01,220 --> 00:04:02,240
I've said a million times

88
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,110
I didn't do it.

89
00:04:03,670 --> 00:04:04,510
Ms. Fei,

90
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,560
I bought a new lip balm, Half Cherry,

91
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,400
for you.

92
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,830
Wear that to go on stage tonight

93
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,680
and you'll outshine everyone.

94
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,600
I outshine others for my performance,

95
00:04:14,030 --> 00:04:15,110
not for my looks.

96
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,560
Is that so?

97
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:17,880
In that case,

98
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,150
don't put on any makeup.

99
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:20,880
Perform onstage without it.

100
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,120
Meng, I'll take it if she won't.

101
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:26,600
I picked up

102
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:28,030
this lip balm for her.

103
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:29,230
If you also want it,

104
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,500
I'll get you one next time.

105
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:34,240
You grab everything that's mine.

106
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,910
Take it if you like it.

107
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,390
No wonder you gave it away to me.

108
00:04:40,390 --> 00:04:41,480
Turns out, the lip balm

109
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,430
had been tampered with.

110
00:04:42,430 --> 00:04:44,150
I didn't even open the box.

111
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:45,310
How could I do that

112
00:04:45,310 --> 00:04:46,150
without touching it?

113
00:04:46,310 --> 00:04:47,910
We all know you're a mutt from Nanwu.

114
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,800
You're full of tricks.

115
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:50,720
Who's a mutt?

116
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,560
You!

117
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,400
You're a mutt!

118
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,670
Stop arguing.

119
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,880
The box doesn't seem to have a hidden switch.

120
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:57,910
Mr. Meng,

121
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,710
where did you buy the lip balm?

122
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:03,000
From the rouge shop

123
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,140
on the west side of the city.

124
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,800
After you bought it,

125
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,820
did you bring it

126
00:05:06,820 --> 00:05:07,760
with you the whole time?

127
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,390
Just now, before I performed,

128
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,200
I put the box on the table over there.

129
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:15,710
That vamp did it.

130
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:16,950
She didn't want me

131
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:18,000
to perform Phoenix Hairpin

132
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:19,320
to outshine her.

133
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,830
Phoenix Hairpin? Did Mother...?

134
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:27,880
Set the lip balm aside for now.

135
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,150
It's almost showtime.

136
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:30,680
Given Yanniang's condition,

137
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,680
she can't sing.

138
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,000
Mrs. Ziyu, we sing

139
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:35,240
with the throat, nose, and stomach,
not the mouth.

140
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,080
I can do it.

141
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,320
But you can't go up there

142
00:05:37,430 --> 00:05:38,270
looking like this.

143
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,240
I have an idea, Yi.

144
00:05:56,830 --> 00:06:01,000
Yes! Good! Great!

145
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:09,640
The Zhu Mansion

146
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:11,160
celebrates this year's Water Festival

147
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,080
with style and grace.

148
00:06:12,870 --> 00:06:13,950
Zhu's celebration

149
00:06:14,310 --> 00:06:15,560
has always been the best.

150
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,030
Of course.

151
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,240
To prepare for it,

152
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,150
I didn't get a good night's sleep.

153
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,000
Didn't Mrs. Ziyu

154
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,840
do all the work?

155
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:26,910
Had Mrs. Lu had such a great daughter-in-law,

156
00:06:27,070 --> 00:06:28,750
Phoenix Hairpin wouldn't have been written.

157
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:29,800
That's too kind of you.

158
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,200
I'm young and ignorant.

159
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,920
Mother planned out everything.

160
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,320
I simply ran errands for her.

161
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,040
Enjoy the show.

162
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,150
It's about to begin.

163
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:41,560
- Great!
- Wonderful!

164
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:45,590
- Beautiful!
- Excellent!

165
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,200
Good!

166
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:05,200
How nice!

167
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:10,840
