169
00:07:14,850 --> 00:07:20,300
♪Spring paints willows green;
palace walls can't confine♪

170
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:25,440
♪East wind unfair♪

171
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:28,620
♪Happy times rare♪

172
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:32,430
♪In my heart, sad thoughts throng♪

173
00:07:32,670 --> 00:07:35,980
♪We've severed for years long♪

174
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:41,740
♪Wrong, wrong, wrong♪

175
00:08:08,440 --> 00:08:11,780
♪Spring is as green♪

176
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:14,960
♪In vain she's lean♪

177
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:22,180
♪Her kerchief soaked with tears,
red with stains unclean♪

178
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:26,200
♪Peach blossoms fall♪

179
00:08:26,460 --> 00:08:29,520
♪Near deserted hall♪

180
00:08:29,970 --> 00:08:36,020
♪Our oath is still there, lo♪

181
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:43,280
♪No words to her can go♪

182
00:08:44,460 --> 00:08:51,050
♪No, no, no♪

183
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,800
- Nice!
- Great!

184
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,440
- Good!
- Beautiful!

185
00:08:56,030 --> 00:08:56,870
How divine!

186
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,150
The Caiyun Troupe

187
00:08:58,150 --> 00:08:59,160
deserves its name.

188
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,150
Mrs. Ziyu, Yan went missing.

189
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,710
- Nice.
- It's really good.

190
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:07,280
What happened?

191
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:08,960
Wasn't she with you the whole time?

192
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,360
I was buying osmanthus cakes.

193
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,730
When I turned around, she was gone.

194
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,480
The streets are packed tonight.

195
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,920
I can't lose her.

196
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:17,160
- Mrs. Ziyu.
- Captain Xie.

197
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:18,790
What's the emergency?

198
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,800
Yan went missing.

199
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,320
Could you help me look for her?

200
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,160
Don't panic.

201
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,870
Let's split up and search.

202
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,400
Sure. Thanks.

203
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:27,080
Azhu, you go that way.

204
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,120
- I'll go this way.
- Yes.

205
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,080
Mr. Yu,

206
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:01,040
why are you watching it from here?

207
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:04,080
It's got a great view.

208
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:08,080
The groom on the boat just now

209
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,440
looked somewhat like you.

210
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,470
Really?

211
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:19,440
Everyone has two eyes and a nose.

212
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,560
Plus, he wore a mask.

213
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,390
We could be similar.

214
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:29,960
What's that?

215
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:38,910
When I came back earlier,

216
00:10:38,910 --> 00:10:40,600
Mr. Meng didn't feel well.

217
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:42,550
He asked me

218
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:44,350
to do that show for him.

219
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:46,800
You had to point out it wasn't him.

220
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,280
Is that so?

221
00:10:57,510 --> 00:10:59,160
Fine, I insisted on doing it.

222
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,710
But why?

223
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:04,680
I couldn't see you marry another man.

224
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:07,680
Pardon? I didn't get it.

225
00:11:13,270 --> 00:11:14,240
I couldn't see you

226
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,360
marry another man

227
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:16,350
even in a show!

228
00:11:36,610 --> 00:11:38,370
Great!

229
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:43,950
Bad news, ma'am.

230
00:11:44,440 --> 00:11:45,510
Ms. Fei sprained her ankle.

231
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,280
What?

232
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,800
Are you alright, Ms. Fei?

233
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,120
What to do?

234
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,280
My performance is next.

235
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:52,710
Have a seat.

236
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,630
Tonight's top priority is

237
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,520
the Water Festival.

238
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:57,360
The ritual dance is most important,

239
00:11:57,360 --> 00:11:58,400
but now, it can't be done.

240
00:11:58,550 --> 00:11:59,830
That'll bring shame

241
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,160
on our whole clan!

242
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,480
You... It's your fault.

243
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,670
You knew you had to dance

244
00:12:05,670 --> 00:12:06,990
but acted so carelessly.

245
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,160
Where's Yi?

246
00:12:08,750 --> 00:12:09,750
Where did she go?

247
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,280
My Lady,

248
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:13,720
we looked all over the Yunshui Tower

249
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,400
but found no sign of her.

250
00:12:15,750 --> 00:12:17,440
She must be avoiding me

251
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:18,830
to make me

252
00:12:19,030 --> 00:12:20,350
clean up the mess.

253
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:21,680
(Where did Yi go?)

254
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,740
(She cares about the Festival the most.)

255
00:12:23,740 --> 00:12:25,090
(She'd never leave without reason.)

256
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,830
(What exactly happened?)

257
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,590
Yan! Yan!

258
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,960
- Ma'am.
- Did you see a little girl?

259
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,920
Did you see her?

260
00:12:32,270 --> 00:12:33,110
No, sorry.

261
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:34,230
Yan!

262
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:36,150
Did you see a little girl?

263
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,470
- I didn't.
- Ms. Fei,

264
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,110
do you have

265
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:40,800
a replacement in your troupe?

266
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:42,440
The ritual dance is the hardest.

267
00:12:42,870 --> 00:12:44,560
No one else can do it.

268
00:12:47,030 --> 00:12:48,720
I happened to learn to dance

269
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:49,800
in my childhood.

270
00:12:50,030 --> 00:12:50,960
When I served

271
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,510
in the Yunshui Tower these days,

272
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:53,750
I saw Ms. Fei dancing.

273
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:54,630
I can give it a try.

274
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:04,630
Beautiful!

275
00:13:04,630 --> 00:13:06,080
It's good, isn't it?

276
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,030
Great!

277
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:07,870
It's nice.

278
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,510
First, Yanniang had an allergy.

279
00:13:15,510 --> 00:13:17,200
Then Ms. Fei sprained her ankle.

280
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,950
Yet she happened to learn that dance.

281
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,440
All that couldn't be a coincidence.

282
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,950
Just now, Ms. Fei said

283
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,870
yam could trigger her asthma,

284
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:28,400
making her too weak to dance.

285
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,240
Qing'er's target

286
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,080
was Ms. Fei

287
00:13:31,090 --> 00:13:32,130
from the very beginning.

288
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:34,320
Yanniang used that lip balm

289
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,800
with yam by accident.

290
00:13:36,050 --> 00:13:37,230
Who knows

291
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:39,400
her scheme actually worked?

292
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,650
She set your sister up

293
00:13:41,650 --> 00:13:43,190
and then stepped forward to save the day

294
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:45,950
to impress the Zhu Clan.

295
00:13:47,200 --> 00:13:49,710
- She's more than she lets on.
