296
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,140
There's no time to lose.

297
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,200
I'll go find my sister.

298
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,600
Watch Qing'er closely.

299
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,590
We'll split up.

300
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,840
Be careful.

301
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:01,390
Yan!

302
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,870
Yinlou!

303
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,160
Miss Si.

304
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:05,680
Did you see Yi?

305
00:14:06,910 --> 00:14:08,240
She thought Yan had gone missing.

306
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:09,550
She must still be looking for her.

307
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,320
Yan, who was there with you?

308
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,440
How did you get lost?

309
00:14:13,790 --> 00:14:14,720
I didn't.

310
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,340
(Yan, Jiang Yi's Daughter)
I fell asleep.

311
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:19,280
Then I saw Mr. Xie after waking up.

312
00:14:20,270 --> 00:14:21,710
She didn't wander away herself.

313
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,320
Someone must've taken her away.

314
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:24,920
But why?

315
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,320
I get it.

316
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:31,560
That was to drive Yi away.

317
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,750
Let's split up

318
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,670
and find her.

319
00:14:34,670 --> 00:14:35,510
Sure.

320
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:36,510
Take Yan with you.

321
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:37,350
- Sure.
- Alright.

322
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,680
Be good, Yan.

323
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:41,960
Let's go.

324
00:14:55,000 --> 00:14:55,840
Yi!

325
00:14:56,510 --> 00:14:57,350
Yi!

326
00:14:59,080 --> 00:15:00,320
(Ms. Fei couldn't perform.)

327
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:01,630
(Qing'er's plan worked.)

328
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:02,990
(Why bother to)

329
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,400
(drive Yi away?)

330
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:11,320
- Great!
- Wonderful!

331
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:18,840
How clumsy!

332
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:22,470
You were so careless.

333
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:24,960
Let's go, Mother.

334
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,300
You need to get changed.

335
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,080
Yan!

336
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:40,590
Yan...

337
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,040
Yi!

338
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:30,630
Yi! Yi!

339
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,230
Wake up!

340
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:34,920
Where's Yan?

341
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:36,200
Where's my daughter?

342
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,040
She's fine.

343
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,200
Don't worry.

344
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:48,080
Yi! What's wrong?

345
00:16:48,270 --> 00:16:49,550
She's having an asthma attack.

346
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:51,230
I brought her here to rest.

347
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,350
An asthma attack?

348
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:53,520
How useless!

349
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,360
She's having it now

350
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,590
