351
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:01,200
I'll call a physician to check her.

352
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:02,950
Don't get changed yet, Mother.

353
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:05,100
Let's take Yi home to make her rest first.

354
00:17:05,200 --> 00:17:06,040
What?

355
00:17:06,350 --> 00:17:08,110
