362
00:17:40,550 --> 00:17:41,480
Mr. Meng.

363
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,240
Close the door.

364
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,720
No one is allowed in.

365
00:17:50,110 --> 00:17:51,150
- Go!
- Yes.

366
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,280
Close the door.

367
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,720
Let no one in.

368
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,560
Yi,

369
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:02,430
what exactly happened?

370
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:05,960
Why is he here?

371
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,350
You tramp!

372
00:18:08,550 --> 00:18:10,960
You had a tryst with a lowly performer

373
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,160
while having your sister

374
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,190
