375
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:15,110
I didn't, Mother.

376
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,720
I came to look for Yan.

377
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:19,110
I don't know why he is here either.

378
00:18:19,960 --> 00:18:21,870
You have to trust me, Ziyu!

379
00:18:22,270 --> 00:18:23,520
Trust you?

380
00:18:24,510 --> 00:18:25,590
He's right here.

381
00:18:26,200 --> 00:18:27,590
We caught you in the act.

382
00:18:28,270 --> 00:18:29,560
Stop denying it!

383
00:18:29,790 --> 00:18:30,830
I'll kill you...

384
00:18:30,830 --> 00:18:31,910
- Lady Zhu.
- You...!

385
00:18:32,030 --> 00:18:33,200
What are you doing?

386
00:18:33,200 --> 00:18:34,280
What am I doing?

387
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:35,840
Ziyu,

388
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:37,310
I'm asking you

389
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:38,720
to get to the bottom of this matter.

390
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,200
If my sister is wronged

391
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,280
for things she didn't do,

392
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,680
you won't look good either.

393
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:44,720
Only the three of you were here.

394
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,670
If Yi didn't do it,

395
00:18:49,400 --> 00:18:50,520
