396
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,110
Si didn't do it.

397
00:18:52,440 --> 00:18:53,870
Really?

398
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,670
Are you also wronged?

399
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:58,190
Did that man

400
00:18:58,350 --> 00:18:59,630
