401
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,000
It was me.

402
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:05,960
I had a tryst with him,

403
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:07,280
not them.

404
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,670
I came to see Meng,

405
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:12,880
but Mrs. Ziyu

406
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:14,190
