407
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:15,520
Meng panicked.

408
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,280
He fell off the bed and fainted.

409
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:19,160
I begged the two of them

410
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,040
to cover for me,

411
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:22,240
