412
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,800
I'm really sorry.

413
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,000
Yi,

414
00:19:36,270 --> 00:19:37,720
I lost my head in a fit of rage

415
00:19:38,830 --> 00:19:40,070
and blamed you

416
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:41,150
before knowing the truth.

417
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:47,670
Once Mr. Meng wakes up,

418
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,910
I'll check everything with him

419
00:19:52,240 --> 00:19:53,240
and clear your name.

420
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:56,320
Are you still doubting me?

421
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:25,870
Qing'er.

422
00:20:26,790 --> 00:20:27,910
Where are you going?

423
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:48,480
Lady Zhu.

424
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:50,760
Young Master Zhu.

425
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:52,080
Mr. Meng,

426
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:55,040
don't be afraid. Tell us

427
00:20:55,510 --> 00:20:56,880
who you came to see

428
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:57,910
for a tryst tonight.

429
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,590
Be honest,

430
00:21:00,240 --> 00:21:01,320
or the Zhu Clan

431
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:03,590
will show no mercy on you!

432
00:21:08,720 --> 00:21:09,800
It was Mrs. Ziyu.

433
00:21:15,830 --> 00:21:17,000
How could it be me?

434
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,830
