441
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:28,760
Nonsense!

442
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,520
When did I fall for you?

443
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,910
Why are you framing me?

444
00:21:33,550 --> 00:21:34,390
Calm down, Yi.

445
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:35,390
Let me ask you.

446
00:21:35,830 --> 00:21:37,040
You said my sister

447
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:39,040
had her maid send you a message, right?

448
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:42,480
Was that maid Qing'er?

449
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:43,560
You knew already.

450
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,430
- Why ask?
- Liar!

451
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:47,670
Qing'er just came to the Zhu's.

452
00:21:47,910 --> 00:21:48,790
Had my sister meant to

453
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:50,070
arrange a secret tryst,

454
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,670
she would've sent her confidant.

455
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,190
Why would she choose Qing'er?

456
00:21:53,590 --> 00:21:54,430
It was her.

457
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,040
She set me up.

458
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:01,280
She used Yan

459
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:02,670
to lure me over.

460
00:22:03,310 --> 00:22:04,310
Yan's over there.

461
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:05,630
- Where?
- Follow me.

462
00:22:11,200 --> 00:22:12,830
(Qian's Nuts)
Yan's inside, Mrs. Ziyu.

463
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,840
Ms. Fei,

464
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:21,950
you claimed

465
00:22:22,270 --> 00:22:24,110
you had a tryst with him

466
00:22:25,350 --> 00:22:26,430
while he said

467
00:22:26,680 --> 00:22:28,760
he came to see Jiang Yi.

468
00:22:30,000 --> 00:22:31,240
Who exactly was it?

469
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:34,110
Bring Qing'er in!

470
00:22:35,920 --> 00:22:36,760
Yi,

471
00:22:38,200 --> 00:22:39,760
I wish I could trust you.

472
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:43,800
We've been married for so long.

473
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:47,110
