474
00:22:48,510 --> 00:22:50,150
Now that your statements don't match,

475
00:22:51,830 --> 00:22:53,190
we'll have to rely on Qing'er

476
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:54,830
to clear your name

477
00:22:56,310 --> 00:22:59,430
and find the evildoer who set you up.

478
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,840
Open it.

479
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:03,240
Get in.

480
00:23:08,350 --> 00:23:09,550
Mrs. Ziyu had me

481
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:10,960
send a message to Mr. Meng

482
00:23:11,270 --> 00:23:12,240
because I was a new maid.

483
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:13,560
I wouldn't draw others' attention.

484
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:14,720
She promised

485
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,270
to send me to Ling'an after tonight,

486
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:18,350
saying it was much better than Lingshui.

487
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:21,240
What are you talking about, Qing'er?

488
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:23,590
I shouldn't have taken you in

489
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:25,320
as Si said.

490
00:23:25,680 --> 00:23:27,320
I never expected a young girl like you

491
00:23:27,590 --> 00:23:29,350
