492
00:23:29,550 --> 00:23:30,720
Mrs. Ziyu,

493
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:32,630
I'm grateful for your kindness,

494
00:23:32,740 --> 00:23:33,590
but this is huge.

495
00:23:33,590 --> 00:23:34,720
I can no longer

496
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:35,630
cover for you.

497
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,550
Young Master, Lady Zhu,

498
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:39,440
I filled in for Ms. Fei to dance just now.

499
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,510
Many people saw me there.

500
00:23:40,510 --> 00:23:42,520
How could I've lured Mrs. Ziyu over?

501
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:43,590
Right.

502
00:23:44,310 --> 00:23:45,590
When I left,

503
00:23:45,720 --> 00:23:46,720
she was dancing.

504
00:23:47,030 --> 00:23:48,080
She couldn't have done it.

505
00:23:49,510 --> 00:23:50,350
Jiang Yi,

506
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,590
how shameless you are!

507
00:23:53,000 --> 00:23:54,880
And here I thought you were decent.

508
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:56,630
You'd never do such indecencies.

509
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:59,190
I couldn't have been more wrong!

510
00:23:59,750 --> 00:24:00,720
At this point,

511
00:24:01,110 --> 00:24:02,350
what else do you have to say?

512
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:04,670
The Zhu Clan's tarnished

513
00:24:04,830 --> 00:24:06,270
all because of you!

514
00:24:06,270 --> 00:24:07,110
Mother!

515
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:08,680
I didn't do it, Mother!

516
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:09,550
You have to trust me!

517
00:24:09,550 --> 00:24:10,560
It wasn't me!

518
00:24:14,350 --> 00:24:15,190
I got you.

519
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:18,150
Qing'er,

520
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,350
I don't know yet

521
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:20,870
how you managed to trick everyone,

522
00:24:21,350 --> 00:24:22,280
but mark my words.

523
00:24:22,790 --> 00:24:24,280
Ruining my sister's name

524
00:24:24,550 --> 00:24:25,910
is ruining her life.

525
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:27,440
You know

526
00:24:27,440 --> 00:24:28,630
how well she treated you.

527
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,880
If you still have a conscience,

528
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,800
tell the whole truth right now!

529
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:35,070
But if you keep lying

530
00:24:35,070 --> 00:24:35,910
and defaming her,

531
00:24:36,270 --> 00:24:37,590
I'll report you to the government!

532
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,520
If the court here can't handle it,

533
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,160
we'll go to court in Ling'an!

534
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:42,000
What?

535
00:24:42,590 --> 00:24:43,590
Your sister committed

536
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:44,790
adultery,

537
00:24:44,790 --> 00:24:46,080
and you're taking it to court?

538
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:47,390
Are you insane?

539
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,240
Lady Zhu,

540
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:50,870
Yi already said

541
00:24:51,310 --> 00:24:52,520
she didn't do it.

542
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,550
No means no, you hear me?

543
00:24:54,550 --> 00:24:55,390
You...

544
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:56,870
Miss Si,

545
00:24:57,920 --> 00:24:59,080
must we go that far?

546
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:01,150
Yi...

547
00:25:02,400 --> 00:25:03,910
No matter what she did,

548
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,430
she's still Yan's mother

549
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:08,080
and my wife.

550
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:11,000
Let's deal with it within our family.

551
00:25:12,020 --> 00:25:12,960
Don't let it out.

552
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:13,910
Don't let it out?

553
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:16,190
Listen carefully, Ziyu.

554
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:17,440
My sister said

555
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:18,880
she didn't do it,

556
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:20,030
so it wasn't her,

557
00:25:20,030 --> 00:25:20,870
understand?

558
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,720
Fine.

559
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:23,640
Let's say she's innocent.

560
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:25,000
It was Qing'er who led her here.

561
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,630
