565
00:25:46,110 --> 00:25:46,950
She...

566
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,520
Two Qing'er?

567
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:52,630
She was the one dancing just now.

568
00:25:54,350 --> 00:25:55,720
I see.

569
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:57,910
They're twins.

570
00:25:58,720 --> 00:25:59,560
Lady Zhu,

571
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:01,070
look at them.

572
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:03,000
One replaced Ms. Fei to dance.

573
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:04,960
The other led my sister here

574
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,400
so that no one would

575
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,240
believe Yi.

